{"id": 1049, "genre": 1001, "title": "在朋友交往尚未熟络之前，你都如何假装？", "description": "凭良心讲，我这辈子很少有这么甜美可爱的时候。（题目来自：Martha Anne）", "record_count": 4200, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703130117bj1JXtvAuQkVWxnL.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-06-11T01:00:26Z", "options": [{"id": 87296, "content": "一般是等待对方发言", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 634400}, {"id": 87552, "content": "假装她说的话，我很感兴趣?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 642199}, {"id": 87808, "content": "假装吃东西斯文", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 642894}, {"id": 87297, "content": "高冷 或者 屌 取决于对方比自己弱还是强", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 607335}, {"id": 87553, "content": "有一种心态，就是要谈女朋友。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 444776}, {"id": 88833, "content": "一直微笑 不说话 然而本人话唠", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1219928}, {"id": 87298, "content": "高冷，或屌丝 取决与对方比自己弱还是强", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 607335}, {"id": 87554, "content": "哦 我不会爆粗口 ～", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 640097}, {"id": 87299, "content": "活泼开朗。熟悉之后整天黑脸玩手机。", "image": "img/option/option/20160702182608rpYeLIDc4UuqhCyo", "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 622880}, {"id": 87555, "content": "假装自己人畜无害", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 59995}, {"id": 87300, "content": "活泼开朗。熟悉之后整天黑脸玩手机。", "image": "img/option/option/20160702182705eZ52wLtvycRKSAMQ", "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 622880}, {"id": 87556, "content": "非常有礼貌非常有教养，能够充分尊重对方的意见。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 642209}, {"id": 87301, "content": "静静的看他们装B。", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 641139}, {"id": 87557, "content": "非常有礼貌非常有教养，能够充分尊重对方的意见。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 642209}, {"id": 87302, "content": "为人民服务的脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 634834}, {"id": 87558, "content": "正襟危坐的微笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 499802}, {"id": 87814, "content": "假装自己很文静", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 642829}, {"id": 87303, "content": "笑～ ", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 608852}, {"id": 87559, "content": "非常有礼貌非常有教养，能够充分尊重对方的意见。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 642209}, {"id": 88839, "content": "刚认识的人都说我文静", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 645111}, {"id": 87304, "content": "有礼貌 装客气 给对方留下好印象", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 641542}, {"id": 87560, "content": "嗯嗯嗯，对对对，你太聪明了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 636214}, {"id": 88840, "content": "附和对方，很少说自己的意见", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 643499}, {"id": 93704, "content": "抑制住内心的小黄", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 653225}, {"id": 87305, "content": "让ta觉得我很喜欢ta", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 628127}, {"id": 87561, "content": "做一个安静的软妹", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 642217}, {"id": 88073, "content": "表现我很稳重", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 311434}, {"id": 115465, "content": "假装自己很高冷", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 755861}, {"id": 87306, "content": "很注意仪表", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 622007}, {"id": 87307, "content": "微笑  点头  是的呀  ?", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 633500}, {"id": 87563, "content": "假装自己很成熟高冷", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 642219}, {"id": 87308, "content": "装腼腆", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 245239}, {"id": 87564, "content": "特别客气，异常小心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 642220}, {"id": 87309, "content": "慢性子模式！熟了之后再也无法启动…", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 570074}, {"id": 87565, "content": "哈，哈哈，哈哈哈?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 642221}, {"id": 87310, "content": "很斯文，其实是疯子", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 641646}, {"id": 87566, "content": "不发脾气", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 642224}, {"id": 87311, "content": "假装自己很洒脱", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 487253}, {"id": 87567, "content": "假装做一个很有涵养的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 641801}, {"id": 87568, "content": "很高冷", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 640224}, {"id": 87313, "content": "假装活泼开朗又热情，好累的喔", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 641656}, {"id": 87569, "content": "摆出一副，送我现金都不爱理你的样子，其实买蛋糕给我，我就屈服了。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 597719}, {"id": 87314, "content": "假装很有共同语言的样子", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 641476}, {"id": 87570, "content": "冷漠", "image": "img/option/option/20160702182531tQ28Yq3DyILUHJv5.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 638921}, {"id": 87571, "content": "礼貌，气质，说话方式，都在变", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 633935}, {"id": 88083, "content": "对他说的一切都表示好有趣。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 643809}, {"id": 104211, "content": "温柔", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 700756}, {"id": 87316, "content": "假装大大咧咧", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 443391}, {"id": 90900, "content": "装作自己很文静 内向 不爱说话", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 651629}, {"id": 87317, "content": "一味装安静美少年", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 641668}]}